{"tid":1869932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真的要改善","createTime":"2020-02-08T12:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T16:24:12.000Z","uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6712ad5561b266c9e10951d57cefab9323cfe0","tid":1869932,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"吳卓燁議員麻煩你學下陳琬琛議員親身 派發口罩比個位老人家  你呢個區係藍屍好多啲區好難先贏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  民賤聯係由94年贏到19年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好藍啲區  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你咁做真係會比民賤聯唱你㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快D滅火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n派口罩反而又出好多事  大埔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心議員認真計劃下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有老人家因此<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">整親</span></span>；最後更因場面混亂而腰斬唔派口罩。吳卓燁喺facebook致歉，但好有霸氣咁反駁不滿者，話如果有街坊不滿，未來「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千萬唔好投我一票</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200207/s00002/1581014435600/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82%E8%85%B0%E6%96%AC-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%80%85-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E6%8A%95%E6%88%91%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link